raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Naomi: Hello everyone!
Naomi: Thanks for your applications and interest in our little club!
Naomi: We're happy you decided to join us!
Suzanna: Wow, quite a large batch this semester
Suzanna: We're about double the size now!
Suzanna: I'm excited to meet you all! So let's do introductions
Suzanna: If you could each tell us a bit about yourself and optionally share a picture of yourself, that would be perfect!
Suzanna: I can start!
Suzanna: I'm Suzanna, I'm the staff coordinator of this club!
Suzanna: Feel free to ask me any questions
Suzanna: Recently, I find myself having a lot more free time so I'm always around!
Suzanna: img: suzanna/5
Suzanna: Forgive me for the overly informal outfit but if you spot me, feel free to say hi!
Caleb: Hiya
- Hi!
	Player: Hi!
- Looking good 👀
	Player: Looking good 👀
	Mabel: Omg babe shush, that's my teacher! 😆
Mabel: Hi Professor!
Suzanna: 😄🧡
Suzanna: I'm so glad you decided to join Mabel!
Mabel: How could I not 😁
Naomi: Heya 👋 I think everyone here knows me already!
Naomi: img: naomi/13
Naomi: Naomi here! I'm acting president of the club
Naomi: That means I do all the paperwork and organize the events for any club collaberations!
Mabel: Naomi! 🥳🩷
- Hi again!
	Player: Hi again!
	Naomi: Hi 😇
- 😉 [if Story.red_heart >= 2]
	Player: 😉
	Naomi: 🤭
Caleb: Hi! Caleb. 
Caleb: Long time member 😄
Caleb: Love photography and I've been doing it since I was in middleschool!
Caleb: Awesome to have so many interested this term
Caleb: Hope we all get along
Suzanna: Caleb is the ace on the team!
Caleb: Ah that's too kind 😅
if Story.has_flag(\"CalebAssist\"):
	Player: Thanks for the help with my submission!
else:
	Mabel: It's true!!
	Mabel: You helped me with my submission 😊
Caleb: Aw shucks, anytime!
Naomi: Thanks babe for being so reliable! 😘
Naomi: Reward later? 😉
Caleb: Jeez Naomi 😀
Naomi: I'm just teasing you 😘
- [...]
Mabel: Hellooo!!
Mabel: I'm Mabel!
Mabel: I'm in Ms Suzanna's class and I like all sorts of arts
Mabel: Uhm, I also like Bond movies too and am a daytime person!
Mabel: img: mabel/83
Mabel: Ack!! My hair's a bit messy 😅
Suzanna: I would have never guessed you like James Bond Mabel!
Mabel: I do!! I watch GoldenEye every weekend 🥹
Player: She sure does! 😆
Mabel: Heyy 😇 It's a good movie!
Suzanna: My ex liked that movie too! 😄
Player: Hi!
- I'm Mabel's boyfriend
	set Story.flag = \"MabelsBoyfriendIntro\"
	Player: I'm Mabel's boyfriend
	Player: Here to support her and the club!
	Mabel: 🥰
	Naomi: You managed to drag him in too huh? 😁
	Mabel: Heyy! He wanted to join 😇
	Suzanna: Wow, what a lucky girl you are Mabel!
	Suzanna: delete: I hope one day to be as lucky as you!
	Naomi: Ms Suzanna! 😆
	Suzanna: Maybe that was a bit unprofessional of me 🤭
	Suzanna: But think of this club as a little family, we sometimes share things from our personal lives!
	Mabel: 😇
	Mabel: That's okay, I did appreciate the complement! 🩷
- I'd like to learn photography too
	Player: I'd like to learn photography too!
	Suzanna: Welcome and I hope you enjoy your time here! 🧡
Alice: Hello..
Alice: Alice
Alice: img: alice/5
Alice: Uhm thats me
Suzanna: Nice to meet you Ms Alice, I've heard a little bit about you!
Player: Hi Alice!
Caleb: Hiya!
Naomi: Glad I was able to convince you to join!
Suzanna: I'm sure Caleb can lend a hand with photography if you're having trouble!
Caleb: Oh for sure, just let me know
Mabel: Nice to meet you Alice! 😁
Mabel: I hope we can become friends!!
Alice: Mhmm.. sure
Naomi: I guess that's everyone
Naomi: Oh hold on, I think we may be missing one
Suzanna: Do we have another member?
Naomi: Seems like it
Naomi: My inbox is flooded with messages from someone 😅
- [...]
System: Paige was added to the group.
Paige: HELLO! HELLO? HELLOOOO~
Paige: You were gonna go on without me!?
Paige: That's sooo heart breaking!! 😭
Paige: img: paige/1
- [...]
Suzanna: Oh!! Seems we have another
Suzanna: Who might you be?
Naomi: Hello Paige 😅
Naomi: You applied but said you weren't sure if you wanted to join so..
Paige: Well I changed my mind 😤
Paige: I see everyone's already introduced themselves sooo 🥺
Paige: Let me tell you all about me 🥰
Paige: I'm Paige!
Paige: img: paige/2
- [...]
Paige: I am interested in fashion, cosplaying, pictures of me (duh), and social scene
Caleb: Hi
Mabel: Nice to meet you 😀
Player: Hi there
Paige: Pleasure to meet any boys 🥰 ... and girls too of course!
Paige: Ex Sorority girl too! 😌
Caleb: 😶
Paige: img: paige/3
Paige: No need to thank me for boosting your club rep
Naomi: Welcome Paige 😅
Naomi: I'm familiar with your story but all the same, we welcome you!
Paige: Awwh thank you babes 🥺
Paige: Hello my dear audience! 🥰
- [...]
Suzanna: Great
Suzanna: Happy to meet everyone here!
Suzanna: I hope we can all get along
Suzanna: Naomi? Are there any events scheduled?
Naomi: Hmm, I'll have to check on that
Naomi: I'll let you all know on Monday how busy this week is.
Naomi: Usually that's my club coordination day!
Mabel: Sounds good 🫡
Player: 👍
Paige: Why don't we gather on Monday and throw a little photoshoot for me? 🥰
Naomi: That's not how we usually do things 😅
Naomi: We prioritize events but sometimes we do have little shoots!
Paige: 🙄
Suzanna: Well thank you all for joining again
Suzanna: I hope you all enjoy your weekends!
Naomi: Keep in touch everyone! We'll have announcements on Mondays!
Mabel: 🥳👏
Caleb: 👍
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
